\n所以我上次跟爸媽說了類似的話，\n結果就大吵架了！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":13,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":13,"voiceId":"episode051-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":13}],"windowDisplayName":"育美","body":"女生要收斂一點，但是我家的女性，\n媽媽一生氣是最危險的。\n上次也是大爆走之後把浴室弄壞了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":13,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":13,"voiceId":"episode051-043","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"心","body":"真糟糕！\n已經修理好了嗎？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":13,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"episode051-044","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":13}],"windowDisplayName":"育美","body":"嗯。\n但是那一天來不及修理，\n所以全家一起去了澡堂","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":13,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":11,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":13,"voiceId":"epi